metadata.description:
The original SKYFISH, gliding over a windy New York City. 

Inspired by the mysterious lunar month of Adar Bet, or Pisces II. This month exists only during a leap year on the lunisolar Hebrew calendar. This rare space in time grants all who are born into it a protective layer of magic, much like the SKYFISH. 

A multimedia animation (video, still photography, illustration) by AA925 in collaboration with 7VW32.

(Duration: 36 sec - Year: 2022 - 1/1)
metadata.name: SKYFISH the OG
